{"thi-ap14:0.1":"Theriapadana ","thi-ap14:0.2":"Ekuposathikavagga ","thi-ap14:0.3":"Ekasanadayikatheriapadana ","thi-ap14:1.1":"“Nagare hamsavatiya, ","thi-ap14:1.2":"ahosim balika tada; ","thi-ap14:1.3":"Mata ca me pita ceva, ","thi-ap14:1.4":"kammantam agamamsu te. ","thi-ap14:2.1":"Majjhanhikamhi suriye, ","thi-ap14:2.2":"addasam samanam aham; ","thi-ap14:2.3":"Vithiya anugacchantam, ","thi-ap14:2.4":"asanam pannapesaham. ","thi-ap14:3.1":"Gonakavikatikahi, ","thi-ap14:3.2":"pannapetva mamasanam; ","thi-ap14:3.3":"Pasannacitta sumana, ","thi-ap14:3.4":"idam vacanamabravim. ","thi-ap14:4.1":"‘Santatta kuthita bhumi, ","thi-ap14:4.2":"suro majjhanhike thito; ","thi-ap14:4.3":"Maluta ca na vayanti, ","thi-ap14:4.4":"kalo cevettha mehiti. ","thi-ap14:5.1":"Pannattamasanamidam, ","thi-ap14:5.2":"tavatthaya mahamuni; ","thi-ap14:5.3":"Anukampam upadaya, ","thi-ap14:5.4":"nisida mama asane’. ","thi-ap14:6.1":"Nisidi tattha samano, ","thi-ap14:6.2":"sudanto suddhamanaso; ","thi-ap14:6.3":"Tassa pattam gahetvana, ","thi-ap14:6.4":"yatharandham adasaham. ","thi-ap14:7.1":"Tena kammena sukatena, ","thi-ap14:7.2":"cetanapanidhihi ca; ","thi-ap14:7.3":"Jahitva manusam deham, ","thi-ap14:7.4":"tavatimsamagacchaham. ","thi-ap14:8.1":"Tattha me sukatam byamham, ","thi-ap14:8.2":"asanena sunimmitam; ","thi-ap14:8.3":"Satthiyojanamubbedham, ","thi-ap14:8.4":"timsayojanavitthatam. ","thi-ap14:9.1":"Sonnamaya manimaya, ","thi-ap14:9.2":"athopi phalikamaya; ","thi-ap14:9.3":"Lohitangamaya ceva, ","thi-ap14:9.4":"pallanka vividha mama. ","thi-ap14:10.1":"Tulikavikatikahi, ","thi-ap14:10.2":"kattissacittakahi ca; ","thi-ap14:10.3":"Uddaekantalomi ca, ","thi-ap14:10.4":"pallanka me susanthita. ","thi-ap14:11.1":"Yada icchami gamanam, ","thi-ap14:11.2":"hasakhiddasamappita; ","thi-ap14:11.3":"Saha pallankasetthena, ","thi-ap14:11.4":"gacchami mama patthitam. ","thi-ap14:12.1":"Asiti devarajunam, ","thi-ap14:12.2":"mahesittamakarayim; ","thi-ap14:12.3":"Sattati cakkavattinam, ","thi-ap14:12.4":"mahesittamakarayim. ","thi-ap14:13.1":"Bhavabhave samsaranti, ","thi-ap14:13.2":"mahabhogam labhamaham; ","thi-ap14:13.3":"Bhoge me unata natthi, ","thi-ap14:13.4":"ekasanassidam phalam. ","thi-ap14:14.1":"Duve bhave samsarami, ","thi-ap14:14.2":"devatte atha manuse; ","thi-ap14:14.3":"Anne bhave na janami, ","thi-ap14:14.4":"ekasanassidam phalam. ","thi-ap14:15.1":"Duve kule pajayami, ","thi-ap14:15.2":"khattiye capi brahmane; ","thi-ap14:15.3":"Uccakulina sabbattha, ","thi-ap14:15.4":"ekasanassidam phalam. ","thi-ap14:16.1":"Domanassam na janami, ","thi-ap14:16.2":"cittasantapanam mama; ","thi-ap14:16.3":"Vevanniyam na janami, ","thi-ap14:16.4":"ekasanassidam phalam. ","thi-ap14:17.1":"Dhatiyo mam upatthanti, ","thi-ap14:17.2":"khujja celapika bahu; ","thi-ap14:17.3":"Ankena ankam gacchami, ","thi-ap14:17.4":"ekasanassidam phalam. ","thi-ap14:18.1":"Anna nhapenti bhojenti, ","thi-ap14:18.2":"anna ramenti mam sada; ","thi-ap14:18.3":"Anna gandham vilimpanti, ","thi-ap14:18.4":"ekasanassidam phalam. ","thi-ap14:19.1":"Mandape rukkhamule va, ","thi-ap14:19.2":"sunnagare vasantiya; ","thi-ap14:19.3":"Mama sankappamannaya, ","thi-ap14:19.4":"pallanko upatitthati. ","thi-ap14:20.1":"Ayam pacchimako mayham, ","thi-ap14:20.2":"carimo vattate bhavo; ","thi-ap14:20.3":"Ajjapi rajjam chaddetva, ","thi-ap14:20.4":"pabbajim anagariyam. ","thi-ap14:21.1":"Satasahassito kappe, ","thi-ap14:21.2":"yam danamadadim tada; ","thi-ap14:21.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","thi-ap14:21.4":"ekasanassidam phalam. ","thi-ap14:22.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","thi-ap14:22.2":"…pe… ","thi-ap14:22.3":"viharami anasava. ","thi-ap14:23.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","thi-ap14:23.2":"…pe… ","thi-ap14:23.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","thi-ap14:24.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","thi-ap14:24.2":"…pe… ","thi-ap14:24.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","thi-ap14:25.1":"Ittham sudam ekasanadayika bhikkhuni ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","thi-ap14:26.1":"Ekasanadayikatheriyapadanam catuttham. "}